scene.message:
Shopkeeper: Howdy. My{nl}
great-grandkid's always in{nl}
your care.{waitkey}{clearbox}I'm watching over you from{nl}
the afterlife. Uhyahyahyahya.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: What's with that old{nl}
man? "The afterlife" — where's{nl}
that, huh.{waitkey}{clearbox}And anyway, why is there a{nl}
pharmacy at the school...?{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Maybe I'll buy up the{nl}
Hanajin Z before school's{nl}
back to normal...{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Nothing but dubious{nl}
medicines... I wonder if{nl}
there's no ill effect on{nl}
the body.{waitkey}{ret}

Frog: Talking to a frog you've{nl}
never met — you must be quite{nl}
bored.{waitkey}{clearbox}For that curiosity, I might{nl}
just give you a free sample{nl}
Satomi Tadashi recommends.{waitkey}{ret}

No way{wait_fr:30}, looks like you've{nl}
got more than I do.{waitkey}{clearbox}Trying to mooch even more —{nl}
you're heartless, you are.{nl}
You'll surely face judgment{nl}
after death.{waitkey}{clearbox}You can just go die. No, no,{nl}
seriously.{waitkey}{ret}

Just kidding{wait_fr:30}. You take all{nl}
three and not even a{nl}
thank-you?{waitkey}{clearbox}Surely{wait_fr:30} you're not swiping{nl}
mini medals and travelers'{nl}
clothes from other people's{nl}
dressers, are you?{waitkey}{clearbox}You can just go die. No, no,{nl}
seriously.{waitkey}{ret}

Frog: Oh my~ so pretty~{color:3}♥{color:0}{waitkey}An impression of Yuka Ayase.{nl}
No, no, seriously.{waitkey}{clearbox}...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}You're always so quiet.{nl}
Here I'm offering comedy, and{nl}
you just put a hand on your{nl}
hip and look down in silence.{waitkey}{clearbox}In tribute to that surliness,{nl}
I might just give you a free{nl}
sample Satomi Tadashi{nl}
recommends.{waitkey}{ret}

Got the "Hangonkou"!{waitkey}{clearbox}Hangonkou — written in kanji,{nl}
it means "soul-summoning{nl}
incense."{waitkey}Very educational, isn't it.{waitkey}{ret}

Just kidding{wait_fr:30}. After making{nl}
me lavish all this on you,{nl}
not one whisper of love?{waitkey}{clearbox}You're of that age now, so{nl}
you ought to learn a little{nl}
about the subtleties between{nl}
man and woman.{waitkey}{clearbox}That is to say{wait_fr:30}{nl}
this frog is a girl{color:3}♥{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}
